    "summary": "Director of software engineering, with many years of coding experience. Long-standing familiarity with managing multi-cultural teams, and delivering complex projects on time.\n\nHands-on practical exposure to AWS (Lambda, API Gateway, Kinesis, SNS, EC2, Route53...) and serverless cloud architectures, alongside CI/CD pipelines (GitHub Actions, CodeFresh...). Daily use of supporting tools such as JIRA, Confluence, GitHub... in the context of SCRUM with two-week sprints.\n\nIn-depth industry expertise and connections in the streaming media world, and the content protection one. Conversant in all things OTT, such as adaptive streaming (MPEG-DASH, Smooth Streaming, HLS, etc.) and content protection mechanisms, including DRM and watermarking.\n\nParticularly versed in being a link between the application development world (coding, management of development teams), and customer relations (pre-sales, requirements gathering, post-sales).\n\nHands-on development competence in C# and the .NET Framework, Node.js (JavaScript, TypeScript), Python. Fluency in C/C++ on Windows platforms.\n\nMaster degree with Eximia cum Laude Approbatur in Computer Science (Tietojenk\u00e4sittelyoppi) from the University of Oulu, Finland.",
